{"tid":1271101,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾庭耀離港大「香港民研」今起獨立運作　僅籌得2萬元","createTime":"2019-07-01T05:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T10:16:00.000Z","uid":265482,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3922b46c8acb5a182b2b8fa4613959b7d688183d","tid":1271101,"uid":265482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21727/鍾庭耀-香港民研-特首民望-21730/鍾庭耀離港大「香港民研」今起獨立運作-僅籌得2萬元?fbclid=IwAR0AhdEs1PsgBZuwb_VcMbxNgqmirQZagf1rqCUayMpbx0G8xX0pxT9Rclk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F21727%2F%E9%8D%BE%E5%BA%AD%E8%80%80-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B-21730%2F%E9%8D%BE%E5%BA%AD%E8%80%80%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94%E3%80%8D%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C-%E5%83%85%E7%B1%8C%E5%BE%972%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0AhdEs1PsgBZuwb_VcMbxNgqmirQZagf1rqCUayMpbx0G8xX0pxT9Rclk&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=2be0ac2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21727/鍾庭耀-香港民研-特首民望-21730/鍾庭耀離港大「香港民研」今起獨立運作-僅籌得2萬元?fbclid=IwAR0AhdEs1PsgBZuwb_VcMbxNgqmirQZagf1rqCUayMpbx0G8xX0pxT9Rclk</a><br />\n<br />\n1991年成立的香港大學民意研究中心（港大民研），今日起脫離港大、獨立運作，取名「香港民意研究中心」（香港民研），繼續由鍾庭耀主理。今年4月23日，鍾庭耀宣布香港民研成立，並眾籌起動經費，目標是600萬港元。惟其後的宣傳工作停滯，兩個多月過去，至今只籌得2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n港大民研在6月下旬已經陸續宣布各項民調暫告一段落，包括政權關注的特首評分、政府民望等，要視乎資金決定延續哪些民調。特首林鄭月娥的評分與民望在6月下旬創歷史新低，「反送中」運動仍在進行中，鍾庭耀希望可以在7月上旬繼續進行這項民調，維持過往約2星期量度一次的頻率，每次所需資金為12萬元，鍾庭耀稱只要7月4日前籌到4萬元，他都會先行「去馬」。<br />\n<br />\n日前的傳媒茶聚上，一眾記者再三向鍾庭耀確認目前籌得款項。鍾又表示，暫未有大金主接觸，將來如有亦不拒絕。茶聚結束，眾人打趣道，可以嘗試到「連登」眾籌，鍾博士聽著略顯茫然，他的同事倒有點興趣。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究中心捐款網站：<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=18faeef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a><br />\n<br />\n幫下鍾博士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398613ea31868a47abfc4683ed1d4a6e6b8b42b6","tid":1271101,"uid":155107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:14:28.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db25137871edbbb6d81cd78407a2dda85aaf89d","tid":1271101,"uid":49044,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:17:50.000Z","msg":"港大根本有心唔比錢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n李國章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f522ee6ef499125e8cd91903234b7922cb3cae8e","tid":1271101,"uid":54563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bdcdf4c670d031545b2ac56e67e8704bc6fab64","tid":1271101,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f942ad2e77cc5ef43835d1974957c1d8e95cba1","tid":1271101,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb28c8ef860eb4a3ab40455e1f298975dcfbb6ef","tid":1271101,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:29:02.000Z","msg":"［向三毛五毛學習，分化藍絲第三集］每次活動後鼓吹失敗主義，用活動手法差異分化群眾，零晨留言引人互屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1271316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1271316</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ed8cee5d8fb7c7051fe9fb56df43c073687c9e1","tid":1271101,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:47:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa84a68a3b6c39906fa4222e577e57aee5e56303","tid":1271101,"uid":155107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-0